{
  "stem": "25835.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "In the meantime, soldier will put to canal-- to canal-- you know what is it-- to other-- to center Warsaw, wounded or not.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And soldier left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I didn't want to go to other part of Warsaw because my mother was already devastated with knowing that my brother is in [NON-ENGLISH] Center.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I stay with my parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And in this moment when these groups came, they start to shoot people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "If somebody was wounded, they shoot in the spot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And everybody who could go was taken out in big column.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we-- we-- we took only with us whatever you can-- everybody can keep in their hand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My mother was very smart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And she gave-- they knew that something could happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And she gave us gold to put all over because she knew that gold could be helpful to survive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We were taken to Pruszkow, close to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then came order.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Immediately, everybody-- because are bandits from uprising-- to concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They put us-- put us to very crowded cattle train-- not train-- no, wagons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And journey start to be.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Or it was on September 1st, or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It doesn't mean-- I was one month in this hell, very close to death, very close to shot, very close.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Very often I was-- like, maybe angel was with me, [LAUGHS] guardian angel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And, you know, when-- they took us with these wagons to, to Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "When we left this wagon-- very crowded, all my family was with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we suppose that will be some, like for human being, but no.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They put us very bad weather, couple of kilometer on foot, very hungry, very upset, [LAUGHS] and very unhappy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "They took us to the big, big place, which greeted us with sign, Arbeit macht frei, you see, big nice sign.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
